<button class="accordion">What is coaching and mentoring in the workplace?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>Coaching and mentoring are development approaches based on the use of one-to-one conversations to enhance an individual's skills, knowledge or work performance.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/collections/coaching-and-mentoring-courses-training-online-accredited" target="_blank"><font color="green"><u> <b>Click here for more Online Coaching and Mentoring Training Courses.</b></u></font></a></p>
