<button class="accordion">What is the goal of coaching and mentoring?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>The goal of coaching and mentoring seeks to build wisdom and the ability to apply skills, knowledge and experience to new situations and processes. The focus is on meeting particular objectives within a set period. Coaching is mainly concerned with performance and the development of specific skills.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/collections/coaching-and-mentoring-courses-training-online-accredited" target="_blank"><font color="green"><u> <b>Click here for more Online Coaching and Mentoring Training Courses.</b></u></font></a></p>
